Most Alacritty users pair it with tmux or zellij. These tools allow you to split your screen into panes or create "tabs" (windows) managed within the terminal itself, rather than by the GUI.

Workflow: Open Alacritty → Start tmux → Ctrl+b then c to create a new window.

